snippet: The United Nations Relief and Works Agency, the body that provides assistance to Palestinian refugees, announced that a two-month strike by its employees in the West Bank had ended.
abstract: United Nations Relief and Works Agency, body that provides assistance to Palestinian refugees, says two-month strike by its 4,500 employees in West Bank has ended.
